com.bmc.arsys.api.apiconverter

Class ArAttachmentInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bmc.arsys.api.AttachmentValue
      • com.bmc.arsys.api.apiconverter.ArAttachmentInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable

    public class ArAttachmentInfo
extends AttachmentValue
    Handles the compress attachment for sending to server, and decompress the attachment for receiving from server. These process does not expose to Jni approach If the compression is handled in the chunking, we skip the compression operation here.
    See Also:
